.token-distribution-2.container(data-aos="fade-right")
  h2 
    span The ArtPro Market
  .chart
    img(src="images/charts/token_distribution_2/chart_3.png", data-rjs="images/charts/token_distribution_2/chart_3@2x.png", alt="")
    ul.list.clearfix
      li.item.item--1
        .item__icn
        .item__title Step 1
        .item__text Buyers search for available work on the platform. Using filters to narrow the search, there is the option to view works only from verified sellers.
      li.item.item--2
        .item__icn
        .item__title Step 2
        .item__text Once they have chosen a piece, the provenance report is downloaded using the APT token. When satisfied, the buyer can add it to the cart.
      li.item.item--3
        .item__icn
        .item__title Step 3
        .item__text Payment is made using APT. Once the checkout is complete, the token is locked into the smart contract. If the vendor is verified, the APT Token will be released straight away.
      li.item.item--4
        .item__icn
        .item__title Step 4
        .item__text Once successful delivery of the art has been confirmed or inventoried in a secure vault, the payment is released to the vendor.
      li.item.item--5
        .item__icn
        .item__title Step 5
        .item__text Feedback is left by both transacting parties for our reputation system and ArtPro receive a small sales commission.